                  <interp inst="t18281204-259-crimeloc1370" type="placeName" value="Devonshire-street, Lisson-grove"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18281204-259-crimeloc1370" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281204-259-off1368 t18281204-259-crimeloc1370"></join>. The prisoner came to lodge there last Saturday four weeks; on the Monday following, we missed these things - she gave a reference as a servant out of place; I missed a bolster, a counterpane, a looking-glass, and a flat-iron - they were a part of the furniture of the room; she was about leaving, and had come in two or three times in a state of intoxication.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18281204-259-person2227">
                  ANN 
                  DAVIS
               <interp inst="t18281204-259-person2227" type="surname" value="DAVIS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18281204-259-person2227" type="given" value="ANN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18281204-259-person2227" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I lodge in this house. The prisoner came there on the Saturday, and slept with me; on the Monday<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182812040129"></xptr>night, when I went up to bed, the bolster was gone away; she was lying across the bed, intoxicated - I asked where the bolster was; she said she had pawned it, but her mis - tress, with whom she had lived, in Windham-street, owed her 19s., and she would get it out the next day, before Mr. Riley came home; she was out all the next day - I said to her, in the evening, "Have you got the bolster?" she said No, her mistress had disappointed her; we did not miss the counterpane till Thursday, nor the glass till Friday - she promised to get them every day, but did not.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18281204-259-person2228">
                  WALTER 
                  FARREN
               <interp inst="t18281204-259-person2228" type="surname" value="FARREN"></interp>
