                     <interp inst="t18281204-259-person2228" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. I have a bolster pawned on the 10th of November, a looking-glass on the 11th, a counterpane on the 12th, and a flat-iron on the 17th; the looking-glass was pawned by the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18281204-259-person2229">
                  THOMAS 
                  HENRY THOMPSON
               <interp inst="t18281204-259-person2229" type="surname" value="HENRY THOMPSON"></interp>
